---
By: Dalai Lama
Source:
  URL: https://twitter.com/DalaiLama/status/979652002014748672
  Locus:
    Date: 30 Mar 2018
---
Change in the world comes from individuals, from the inner peace in
individual hearts. Just as ripples spread out when a single pebble is
dropped into water, the actions of individuals can have far-reaching effects.
